{"type": "article", "id": 41989, "title": "东京要开 VR 主题乐园，以及，阿迪出了天鹅绒拖鞋 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-06-15T03:17:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 2145, "name": "Converse"}, {"id": 3132, "name": "Emilio Pucci"}, {"id": 4035, "name": "拖鞋"}, {"id": 11450, "name": "HTC Vive"}, {"id": 41466, "name": "VR 乐园"}, {"id": 1331, "name": "雅诗兰黛"}, {"id": 2968, "name": "Mulberry"}, {"id": 7973, "name": "Inditex"}, {"id": 41467, "name": "Miley Cyrus"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170615095216wa2nv7rNE1q6hmye.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/inditex-net-profit-rises-18-in-q1-10913745/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>西班牙零售集团 Inditex 发布第一季度财报，利润上涨了 18%</strong></a> | 在截止至 4 月 30 日的第一季度，ZARA 的母公司、西班牙零售集团 Inditex 的销售额上涨了 14%，至 55.7 亿欧元。净利润则上涨了 18%，至 6.45 亿欧元。Inditex 最新数据显示，该集团目前在 93 个国家地区拥有 7385 家店铺。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/beauty-features/lauder-retires-estee-edit-10911995/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>雅诗兰黛宣布关闭产品线 Estee Edit </strong></a>| 这条产品线创办于去年，主要在社交媒体上传播，由网红 Kendall Jenner 代言，号称是雅诗兰黛专门为千禧一代开设的产品线。Estee Edit 进驻丝芙兰， 82 个 sku 里面有 72 个都是美妆产品。雅诗兰黛称，砍掉这条线原因是销售业绩并不理想。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/business-features/mulberry-profits-sales-climb-recasts-marketing-strategies-10914124/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>英国奢侈品牌 Mulberry 发布全年财报，销售额上涨 7.8%</strong></a> | Mulberry 最新财报显示，在截止至 3 月 31 日的 12 个月内，该品牌的销售额上涨 7.8% 至 1.68 亿英镑，净利润暴涨了 86%，至 500 万英镑。该品牌的 CEO Thierry Andretta 称，将在下一个财年加快对亚洲市场的扩张。 </p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>当红流行歌手<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/6/miley-cyrus-joins-converse-yes-to-all\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Miley Cyrus 正式加入 Converse</a>，鼓励年轻一代挺身而出，直面 LGBTQ 群体所面对的不公正现象。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615101303N5KUWOIfQ4hb9S2k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615101303bd9ELYzAWiB4tH7h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615101309f965byBNlpeOAW3c.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/06/14/adidas-adilette-mystery-blue-green/\" rel=\"nofollow\">阿迪达斯经典拖鞋 Adilette 升级</a>。这一次带来的最新版本共有两款颜色，鞋底与鞋面均采用了天鹅绒材质，定价为 45 美元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706151019014LBtQ9ZDHUzoPRyq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615101900tOywgJfV07L3rEcu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615101859RPmuCWOZS62j5Ehk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615101859z5KaSkhWFdVQ3fyi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615101901U36cXjqxenkbNIu1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615101859Zy7AkpVtjSzRnBDE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615101900agHrX0Y1f6Zoq8vE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615101900anD7iIpwdToQ8xb9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>HTC Vive 和万代公司合作，要在东京新宿开设一个虚拟实境主题乐园 <a href=\"https://vrzone-pic.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">VR ZONE SHINJUKU</a>。该乐园占地约 3500 平方米，提供超过 15 个以上的 VR 体验内容，包括《Mario Kart Arcade GP》、《新世纪福音战士『魂之座』》、《七龍珠『秘伝かめはめ波』》、《攻壳机动队 ARISE Stealth Hounds》及《GUNDAM『台场强袭』》等游戏大作。该乐园将于 7 月 14 日在日本新宿正式运营，6 月 16 日开放官网预约，入场门票和 VR 体验馆将分开收费。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615101923CDQw1dXJZ4078unq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707143\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615101923bRFzjKLvIYN12nsW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707143\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615101923uDA0oVCcWUR1hnZP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707143\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615101926QhHBw0vXiDlAPeIt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.707143\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>喜欢 90 年代日本街头风格的话，不妨来看看澳大利亚新晋街头品牌 <a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/06/14/okuh-studios-topman/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Okuh Studios 为 Topman 最新打造的这个以日本漫画为灵感的系列</a>。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615101959nIUbNs19HhcAdFgw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615101959KIkBZJtgevyfPFX6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706151019595Q09SrcuLXUa7oAj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706151019599AChkHwpZonYczqO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102000XIeaTurYwtoVGKsm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615101959BsbiOrKZF4U9YaPn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615101959PxD2ubUvesczBO7n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102000UbHf8lRPQItOokw6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102023BUjCZRcDI4kqhSGO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/shoes/emilio-pucci-sneakers-of-the-world/\" rel=\"nofollow\">意大利品牌 Emilio Pucci 最近推出了一个 Sneakers of the World 系列</a>。该系列以伦敦、纽约、香港、巴黎、迪拜、莫斯科、首尔、佛罗伦萨等 11 个城市为灵感，鲜艳的色彩配上荷叶边细节装饰，时尚感十足。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102049dGsxvRcV1lPBCXgh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706151020504LWRS3azxgKEicPH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102051E5BQut0gDGCScUmP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102051MavGUL7hRFiVZxdm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102052xqHgE4TdPlGeIJc7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102053VOEnLyGZAQHW4tbU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102053iWwI7rSqjnVPb8cB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102053uM7C6HbQj3zBs4pL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102105HTWenDK7msPxkFRG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102105Xpznvy1LNFRV3rAu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102105QKUfd0Ju3cREhoBP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102106f9iTusvWhZ7tlz53.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102106KnJzxqMbAel38D0i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102106ZoFSMHJrkpI9aTVX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102106Alyg5IDKJGtY4kmx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102107ZGu5VF8XDNaJ32AQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102107lvMNm8VsDJF0ndYk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170615102109xTEipGPA4F5vOVDg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706151021090VGF2mE98ZuOfDI6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/06/14/adidas-adilette-mystery-blue-green/\" rel=\"nofollow\">highsnobiety</a></p>"}